data.description: Nestled within the charming Wayne Terrace neighborhood in Jesup, GA, this delightful brick residence exudes timeless elegance with a contemporary twist. Meticulously renovated within the last two years, the home seamlessly marries modern amenities with the enduring allure of its ranch-style architecture. Step inside to discover a single-level layout designed for effortless living, ideal for families and those preferring the simplicity of one-story accommodation. The foyer welcomes you with a sense of openness, leading gracefully into a light-filled living space. The kitchen boasts white cabinetry with sleek stainless steel appliances, and ample amount of cabinet and counter space. Adjacent to the kitchen, the dining area provides a convenient setting for hosting intimate dinners or lively get-togethers. Three generously proportioned bedrooms await, each boasting ample closet space and an abundance of sunlight to enhance comfort and relaxation. The two bathrooms have been thoughtfully updated. Outside, the allure continues with a sprawling backyard enveloped in beautiful landscaping, complemented by a pergola showcasing a recently installed swimming pool (2 years old)-an inviting oasis for those upcoming summer months. Fully fenced for privacy and security, the yard offers peace of mind for families with children and pets alike. Embodying the perfect fusion of contemporary convenience and traditional charm, this impeccably updated ranch-style abode awaits your personal touch, promising a lifestyle of comfort and refinement for years to come. Call your favorite Realtor today.
